          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780684862712" href="/book/show/780682.Pay_It_Forward">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/229001-rose-ann?shelf=borrowed-from-library">borrowed-from-library</a>, 
