        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer885807805" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14391815325787186626">This is the first book I’ve read by Catherine Ryan Hyde and loved it. It tells about a boy with an enormous heart and witty intelligence. He creates a project that will change the world, though he doesn’t know that the results will truly be worldwide. It makes you appreciate the simple creative minds of children. Aside from that, there is a romantic tie that flows with the story to give the book a combination plot. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


